  "prompt": "Are maps of New York City free?",
  "response": "Yes, many maps of New York City are available for free. You can find free maps at various locations, such as:\n\n1. **Tourist Information Centers**: These centers often provide free maps for visitors.\n2. **Subway Stations**: MTA (Metropolitan Transportation Authority) stations typically have free subway maps.\n3. **Online Resources**: Websites like NYC.gov and various tourism websites offer downloadable maps.\n4. **Mobile Apps**: Many apps provide interactive maps of the city, often for free.\n\nHowever, some specialized or detailed maps, such as those focusing on specific neighborhoods or attractions, may be sold at bookstores or shops.",
